Jepe's Z-Bundle IV
------------------
 
https://cdn.pximg.xyz/0dc69cb0984e9e4d2602b35af0514a6b.jpg

Jepe's Z-Bundle IV is the fourth Ultimate Collection of 2D Billboard Special Effects for your 3D applications containing everything you need to enhance your art work right within your 3D scene.

Please see each product's page for details.

Included are the latest Iray versions of the products (Daz only). 

This bundle includes:

Jepe's FlameZ III DF - www.daz3d.com/catalog/product/view/id/19045
Jepe's PlateZ - www.daz3d.com/catalog/product/view/id/14729
Jepe's PlateZ II - www.daz3d.com/catalog/product/view/id/14921
Jepe's PlateZ III - www.daz3d.com/catalog/product/view/id/18522
